The official Association of Computer Science Students at the ETH Zurich (VIS) was founded in 1984 and is a student association of the Association of Students at the ETH (VSETH).
tags.name: VIS - Verein der Informatikstudierenden

tags.description: GECo, the Gaming and Entertainment Committee of VSETH has the mission to support the gaming community at ETHz & UZH. This entails organizing social gaming nights, board game days, RPG days, public viewings and a big LAN party once every semester.
tags.name: VSETH GECo

tags.description: We are a committee of VSETH whose mission it is to support the Linux & FOSS community at ETH & UZH. We organize FOSS & Linux related events & workshops and have biweekly get-togethers. Feel free to come by and say hi.
tags.name: VSETH TheAlternative
